==English==

===Etymology===
Compare '''1769''', Oxford Standard text, ''[[s:Bible (King James)|King James Bible]]'', ''[[s:Bible (King James)/Matthew|Matthew]]'', xxiii, 3 — ''For they bind heavy burdens and grievous to be borne, and lay them on men's shoulders; but they themselves will not move them with one of their fingers.''

